data.description: *Generous Price Adjustment made 12/18/23* Welcome to this spacious and inviting home located in Weaverville. With ample space and a workshop in the garage, this property is perfect for those who love to work and create. This home has been well taken care of, and contains craftsman accents & custom woodwork throughout. Additionally, a separate entrance to the office provides flexibility and convenience for professionals or those seeking a private workspace. Step outside, and enjoy the view of the treetops from one of the large decks. The highlight of this remarkable home is the 20’x40’ in-ground pool, offering a refreshing retreat during the warm summer months. The property also has a lower entrance leading to a pole barn & a large fire pit. Being conveniently located near I-26 grants easy access to nearby amenities, making this property an ideal choice for those seeking the best of both comfort and convenience.
